data.description: Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this meticulously upgraded home where no detail was overlooked.  Impact Windows and doors ensure both safety and energy efficiency.  Crown molding elegantly frames each room adding a touch of sophistication.  The kitchen features recessed lighting, porcelain floors and dove-tail soft close drawers, making it a dream.  Additional upgrades include w/h, custom blinds and knock down textured walls throughout. The living room, bedrooms, and back Florida room have all been enhanced with new flooring, providing a fresh & modern look. The separate laundry room offers added convenience, with ample storage space and a side entrance.  Gutters and fully fenced backyard with brand new sod. Carport and plenty of parking options.  Agents please see BK remarks.
